Ask HN: Book recommendations about the history of the internet
text:
Hello HN,

I would love to hear your recommendations on books about the history of the internet.

The topic is broad and vague, but I'd generally be interested in the different protocols, key people, how it was used throughout time, browsers even, and whatever else that you think might be related.

I am not in CS/IT (I'm an academic scientist) so it wouldn't have to be overly technical, but I do appreciate some detail.

Many thanks!

Ask HN: Anyone had their Cloudflare credit card information stolen recently?
text:
I just noticed that there was an unauthorized charge on my company debit card that was only used at Cloudflare.

Thankfully it was declined because they had the wrong expiration date, but it's really strange to me, especially since we haven't used that card in months (we use one card per merchant, this one was dedicated to CF), so I'm really curious to see if anyone had that happen recently? Whoever found the number tried to spend 15$ at zulily which I'm guessing they are using to test the card.
